# basePath RS-1A

:: diveSite.probe
@trigger    PlayerEnterRegion
@when    scene:name == "RS-1A", scanned:RS-1A.probe, regionId = "probeScan"
{@probe}    Beep, boop.. Welcome to Dive Site A! Which critter do you want me to check?
$call Probe->AskForBestiaryEntry temp:critterImproveId
$if !temp:critterImproveId
    {@probe}    Looks like it doesn't need any additional data yet.
$else
    {@probe}    Collecting data...{wait [3]}{var-s temp:critterImproveId}s' data is finished!
    $call Probe->ImproveRules
$endif